Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:25.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}絢爛奪目 不堪直視
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:31.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}初始不期而至 迅如暴風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:35.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被你的眸 深深吸入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:41.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}初感的衝動 因為你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:46.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想窺探 想知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:55.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}未知的你 真實的心請允許我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:58.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}數著星星的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:00.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你與我邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:03.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}兒時仰望天際
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虔誠祈禱的我已翱翔在天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.30,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}胸中栽培夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思念孕育力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:13.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}願與你攜手去往無限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:17.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}成為導航未來之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,身為Capital衛隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,自然想刺探亞美利亞宇宙艦隊的實情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,為此既要撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,又要和海盜和睦相處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我無法欺騙自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那確實是教官的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我清清楚楚地…聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,面具部隊的強襲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏不妨告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,實不相瞞 我是昆達拉出身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,據我所知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,入選的各位無一例外是昆達拉出身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼是昆達拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,據說是舊世紀時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,被視作「活乾糧」的…劣等人種的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這艘Garanden號的面具部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果立下戰功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,昆達拉將贏得尊重！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 終有一天成為Capital塔之主！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個道理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,面具部隊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Elf·Bullock隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,剿滅宇宙海盜！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快回來 別添亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,放下槍座
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續放 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,再放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅說 想在G-Self裏睡午覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼勸都不聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好 有事喊我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這個叫拉萊雅的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,既然這麼迷戀G-Self…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}快看 開始充氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}這玩意兒真能冒充Megafauna？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}第一站點 Coriole
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}要亞美利亞閉嘴還不簡單…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}可惡 體重增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}胖了還怪慣性重力？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝長期惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,也感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然讓那種東西駐紮在城裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼雙體機可以在這裏飛行？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,茹甘！簡直目中無人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,徵用最大的廣場？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是Capital政府的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,茹甘這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,茹甘司令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏可不是Capital軍的前線基地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只是搬運食物 水和壓縮空氣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,司令 發現宇宙海盜艦船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是Megafauna嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,海盜船…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對 就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼模糊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大氣晃動影響 如果繼續修正…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯就在那裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,身為運營長官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很早就想一睹海盜船的尊容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉失陪 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,貝克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,昆珀上校調來的Garanden號到哪裏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這能看出什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是它沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,部隊所到之處軍艦伺候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,茹甘司令還真是心思縝密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那是Megafauna的仿真氣球？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是總監旗下的部隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,來這裏幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,補給呀 補給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,送G系列部件什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 G-Self的專用宇宙背包 到貨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？這強襲背包還沒試射呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哈朋先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,早就知道會是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,又要我們實戰測試 真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,機槍塔是修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可是本土送來的補給才剛到位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:08:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他們說艦隊發射入軌的時間提前了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就算這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,依次類推 我們只能提前執行佯攻計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Montero和G-Self在那上面做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,克裏姆中尉在調試和Belay的並聯繫統
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才放的仿真氣球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真能瞞過Capital軍的監視？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,充其量自我安慰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟通訊更不靠譜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,只有等他們親手送來命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,順便用Belay和Ladle 捎些貨物過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看這雙你最喜歡的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,它會讓你清醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡的眼睛想看 啾啾咪也想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因為它正看著拉萊雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啾啾咪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啾啾咪和我都想看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅駕駛它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,駕駛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啾啾咪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 你能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,能用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉 門開著！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是大氣層滑翔機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,滑翔機？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔為應對各種突發狀況做好了準備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不觸犯禁止發展舊科技的禁忌嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,凡具有歷史價值的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,允許維護並保持其機能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,返回地面用的滑翔機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如今有何用武之地？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有時可執行偵查任務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,頂罩！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉 請去氣壓門內避難
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,艙門要開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那個笨女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！開了！開了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？為什麼艙門會開？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,貝克上尉來電
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,韋米特長官乘坐的滑翔機被意外彈射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,已經離開無線電範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,還有人在給那東西做日常維護？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,滑翔機一旦發射可能有去無回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 如果返地角度出現偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,機體就會在大氣層中化為灰燼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 好歹算是矇混過關
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有太空服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在下降？還是升高？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,由拉萊雅駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你做到了 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅 我回Montero上去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,讓G-Self帶上步槍 朝著Belay的前方好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,B！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,啾啾咪和我都在看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在看？啾啾咪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人就在島嶼的另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Elf·Bullock全隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,測試光束軍刀發振情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,發現不明飛行物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,伊賽拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,確認與仿真氣球的位置關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,隨時通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,警報在響
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 拉萊雅醬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,能做個持盾動作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,盾？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,盾…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,動作看起來挺正常啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的！是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啾啾咪看 是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我也出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才在吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？他們說G-Self已經出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,空中變形 快！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,島對面來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,上面的事你得去問上面人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,還在說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,進餐也是駕駛員的重要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,請盡快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我用Arcane出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有機體給貝魯利·賽納姆駕駛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,甲板上的Ladel上停著一架Gehennam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,給他用沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他的實力你應該知道才是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,跑去甲板上的Gehennam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,又刁難人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladel的駕駛員是金格爾 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你留步！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好好幹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gehennam是亞美利亞的正規軍機體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利·賽納姆 登機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:14:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是通用系統 你會擺弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,保護飛船！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,「包在我身上」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要說這種話 起碼還得兩三年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,叫貝魯利的 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,固定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓我試射下光束步槍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那就現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不朝天上開？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不怕被敵人看見光束嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,已經撒了米諾夫斯基粒子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哦…收到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,角度…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣應該可以對付過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 忘了帶貝魯喜歡的香蕉和桂皮小鬆餅！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,機體的耐熱和密封性能沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Cord…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,讓機體回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽見克裏姆中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,用哄小孩的口吻說「拉萊雅醬」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅在駕駛席上？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她明明還沒恢復記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,接觸線路 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利·賽納姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒瘋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,帶這麼大的步槍出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,才不聽你指手畫腳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,西面來的不明飛行物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是Capital軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍根本沒有海上兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可現在他們來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅醬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,蹲下 會摔下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,發光了 它在發光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,發光？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,和不明飛行物交火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪個被打中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,發光了！啾啾咪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮眼睛先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你來了！G-Self
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,還想變形不成！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:17:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉險些俘虜的那架機體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍還沒對它完成分析
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,必須奪取！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,亞美利亞的機動戰士算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,淹…淹死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,啾啾咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 根本不會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,放鬆點別緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,掩護克裏姆的Montero
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯 貝魯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,林 林 林 林
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 啾啾咪想看外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,外面？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看它多高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小眼睛是紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 她就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可以 那你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我去幫中尉和艾達小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,還不給我死！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:19:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看來機動戰士形態無法飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不能放跑受傷的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,擺脫不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,來增援的新型機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍竟然有那種編隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,裝腔作勢的亞美利亞精英
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 精英來扮海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,被瞄準了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 克裏姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這個大傢伙歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,被砍…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,隊…隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self 從海裏出來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 接觸線路打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐 用助推器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利·賽納姆 這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐 一起迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self不是給海盜用的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你們不明白G-Self從天而降意味著…什麼嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,擊落它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,雷哈頓！還能控制
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,還不下海！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,防…防禦罩？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就算這樣 逮住它也只是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利需要掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下 別亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self背後不長眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退吧 大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你也受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那就把你們一網打盡！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,亞美利亞軍的援軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下 是Armorzagan！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,父親連那種東西也允許他們開發？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,亞美利亞軍的機動堡壘？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那支部隊還沒全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯應該就在那座島的某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒來得及說明來自宇宙的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.88,0:24:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,又遭到變形機動戰士部隊的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,為擊退他們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,必須使用粉紅色背包出戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.29,0:24:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達的父親這樣說道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.57,0:24:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 快來救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.82,0:24:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 G之復國
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.61,0:24:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,父與母與面具
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.83,0:24:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,別邊走邊看哦
